author: Daniel Greene
description:
AI vs The Mouse?! In this episode of Fantasy News, we cover Disney’s lawsuit against Midjourney, a massive new licensing deal for Sarah J. Maas, The Wheel of Time summary update, the Malazan: Bonehunters re-release, a new Murderbot title from Martha Wells, and the Elden Ring movie updates you didn’t know you needed—plus Dungeon Crawler Carl, Vinland Saga, Death Stranding 2, and more!
